.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There are 6 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese, indonesian, mexican, argentine, spanish
House: modern, cottage, futuristic, ranch-style, tower, gothic-revival
1. the futuristic house is the mexican##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the modern house##1
3. the tower house is on the left of the indonesian##1
4. the ranch-style house is the chinese##1
5. the pakistani is the modern house##1
6. the cottage house is between the modern house and the spanish##2
7. the chinese is on the left of the spanish##1
8. the futuristic house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Nationality        | chinese    | spanish | indonesian | pakistani | argentine | mexican   |
| House   | ranch-style | tower        | cottage  | modern     | gothic-revival  | futuristic |

