.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, mirinda, milk, 7up, coffee
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, rose, poppy, azalea, zinnia
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growszinnia is the person drinking water##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who growslily##1
7. the person who growsrose is the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking milk and the person who growszinnia##2
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | coffee | 7up  | milk      | mirinda | water  |
| Flower   | lily  | rose    | poppy | daisy | azalea | zinnia |

