.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  electrician, software-developer, dancer, doctor, librarian, paramedic
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, cricket, golf, badminton, handball
1. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is between the librarian and the doctor##2
4. the doctor is the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the paramedic is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the librarian is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is badminton##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Job       | paramedic | doctor | electrician | librarian | dancer | software-developer |
| Sport   | cricket | handball    | badminton  | climbing    | golf    | skiing    |

