.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
6 different pets are kept: frog, cat, dog, goat, goldfish, pony
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, zombie, scientific, martial-arts, animation, fantasy
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching romance movies##2
4. the owner of the goat is the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the goldfish##2
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Pet           | goat | pony | goldfish | dog | cat | frog |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific   | martial-arts   | zombie         | romance    | fantasy     | animation     |

