.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, october, december, may, january, july
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, begonia, balloon-flower, lily, daffodil
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person who growszinnia is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Birthday   | april   | january  | october | may | july | december     |
| Flower   | orchid | zinnia | daffodil    | lily | balloon-flower | begonia |

