.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, ship, scooter, motorbike, roller
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, january, june, october, july, december
1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the subway##2
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the scooter and the person who's birthday is in march##2
9. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Transport   | ship | roller | scooter   | snowmobile | subway | motorbike |
| Birthday           | march  | october   | june | january | december       | july |

