.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, january, june, november, december, september
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, baccarat, swisher, montecristo, old-henry, vegafina
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is the old-henry-smoker##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the old-henry-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 6. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 7. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is between the prince-smoker and the person who's birthday is in january##2
10. the person who's birthday is in november is the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Birthday         | september   | december | june       | november | may    | january |
| Cigar   | baccarat | old-henry  | swisher | prince      | montecristo | vegafina        |

