.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
There 6 different types of food: tomato, pumpkin, mango, lemon, eggplant, kiwi
City: venice, nizza, miami, colone, paris, san-francisco
 1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 3. the person eating pumpkin is the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person eating mango is between the person eating lemon and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
 5. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person eating eggplant##2
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 7. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person eating tomato##1
10. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Food           | pumpkin      | lemon | mango | tomato   | kiwi  | eggplant |
| City   | colone | venice  | nizza             | san-francisco | miami | paris       |

