.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding, soccer, sailing, badminton, water-polo
6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, mouse, dog, hamster, bird
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is sailing##2
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the dog is the person who's sport is rugby##1
8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Sport          | soccer | snowboarding | rugby | badminton    | water-polo | sailing |
| Pet   | mouse     | bird | dog   | lizard | guinea-pig | hamster |

