.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, lemonade, tea, fanta, sprite
6 different games are played: poker, whist, canasta, monopoly, mah-jongg, billiard
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person playing billiard is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person drinking milk##2
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person drinking sprite and the person playing poker##2
 4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is between the person playing canasta and the person drinking lemonade##2
 6. the person drinking tea is the person playing whist##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Beverage   | tea     | iced-tea | fanta   | lemonade     | sprite       | milk       |
| Game    | whist | monopoly   | poker | mah-jongg | billiard | canasta |

