 4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating blueberry is the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person eating spinach is the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person eating orange is the person eating orange##1
 8. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Food   | plum | blueberry    | spinach     | tomato      | orange    | cucumber |
| Transport   | subway | skateboard | ship | airplane | trike | boat  |

